original_title: Superman vs Spider-Man XXX: An Axel Braun Parody
overview: When Doc Ock and Lex Luthor join to defeat their nemesis, Spidey and the Man of Steel meet for the first time and must work together to foil the evil duo's nefarious plans for world domination.
title: Superman vs Spider-Man XXX: An Axel Braun Parody
